1. Install Megasync
2. Install packages
    $ sudo apt-get install keepassx git vim gnome-tweaks vlc
3. Configure GIT
    $ apt-get install libsecret-tools
    $ git config --global user.name "Daniel Buchan"
    $ git config --global user.email "clone@myself.com"
    $ git config --global --unset credential.helper
    $ git config --global credential.helper /usr/libexec/git-core/git-credential-libsecret
4. Log in to github and clone this repo
    $ mkdir Code
    $ cd Code
    $ git clone https://github.com/DanBuchan/setup_linux.git
5. Install VSCode from the .deb https://code.visualstudio.com/download
    $ sudo apt install code*.deb
6. Open Setting and connect to WiFi
7. Open settings and adjust langauge and screen size to 100%
   In Multitasking activate Hot Corner
8. Open gnome-tweaks and increase Fonts -> Size -> Scaling Factor to 2.0
9. Log in Mozilla Account in Firefox
10. Log in to Amazon account
11. Log in to Reddit
12. Install new Gnome extension manager
    Add Frippery Panel Favourites
    Add clipboard Indicator
    Add Hide Activities Button
    Turn off Ubuntu Dock
    Turn On Window List
    Turn on Apps menu